text: Bought Alison Angrim's Confessions of a Prairie Bitch at Barnes & Noble tonight (thank you, 20% off coupon). Looking forward to the read.
#fridayreads  Confessions of a Prairie Bitch " by Alison Arngrim (aka @arngrim aka Nellie Oleson from Little House). Stellar so far!"
I think CONFESSIONS OF A PRAIRIE BITCH by Allison @Arngrim is the best memoir I've read since Jeanette Wall's THE GLASS CASTLE.
How weird is it that the same day I finish  Confessions of a Prairie Bitch " by @Arngrim a 97 year old tells me its good to be a bitch hahaha"
